attributes.title: AP WIZARD - Execute Template Configuration
attributes.code:
<?php 

$guzzleClient = new \GuzzleHttp\Client(['base_uri'=> $_SERVER['HOST_URL'],'verify' => false]);
$guzzleOptions['headers']['Accept'] = 'application/json';
$guzzleOptions['headers']['Authorization'] = 'Bearer ' . getenv('API_TOKEN');
$guzzleApi = '/api/1.0/collections/guided-template';

try {
    $guidedTemplateId = $guzzleClient->request('GET', $guzzleApi, $guzzleOptions);
    $collectionId     = json_decode($guidedTemplateId->getBody()->getContents());
} catch (\Throwable $th) {
    return [
        'errorCode' => $th->getCode(),
        'errorMessage' => $th->getMessage()
    ];
}
$recordInfo['userGroups'] = $data['userGroups'];
$recordInfo['glCollection'] = $data['glCodeIdCollection'];
$recordInfo['assignedEmail'] = $data['assignedEmail'];

$process_launchpad_id = $data['process_launchpad_id'];
$guzzleApi = '/api/1.0/processes/' . $process_launchpad_id;
$res = $guzzleClient->request("GET", $guzzleApi, $guzzleOptions);
$process = json_decode($res->getBody(), true);
$guzzleApi = '/api/1.0/collections/' . $collectionId . '/records';
if (isset( $process['properties']['helperProcessRequestId'])) {
    $helperProcessRequestId = $process['properties']['helperProcessRequestId'];
    $guzzleApi .= '?pmql=data.helperProcessRequestId%20=%20%22' . $helperProcessRequestId . '%22';
    
    try {
        $res = $guzzleClient->request('GET', $guzzleApi, $guzzleOptions);
        $existingRecordRes = json_decode($res->getBody(), true)["data"];
        $existingRecordID = $existingRecordRes[0]["id"];
        $recordInfo['helperProcessRequestId'] = $helperProcessRequestId;
        $guzzleApi = '/api/1.0/collections/' . $collectionId . '/records/' . $existingRecordID; 
        $guzzleMethod = "PUT";
    } catch (\Throwable $th) {
        return [
            'errorCode' => $th->getCode(),
            'errorMessage' => $th->getMessage()
        ];
    }
} else {
    $recordInfo['helperProcessRequestId'] = $data["_request"]["id"];
    $guzzleMethod = "POST";
}
$guzzleOptions['json'] = $recordInfo;

try {
    $res = $guzzleClient->request($guzzleMethod, $guzzleApi, $guzzleOptions);
} catch (\Throwable $th) {
    return [
        'errorCode' => $th->getCode(),
        'errorMessage' => $th->getMessage()
    ];
}

if ($res->getStatusCode() == 201 || $res->getStatusCode() == 204) { 
    return [
        "setupComplete" => "yes",
        "helperProcessRequestId" => $recordInfo['helperProcessRequestId']
    ];
}

attributes.code:
<?php 

use GuzzleHttp\Client;

$apiHost = getenv('API_HOST');
$apiToken = getenv('API_TOKEN');
$client = new Client([
    'headers' => [
        'Authorization' => "Bearer {$apiToken}",
        'accept' => 'application/json',
    ],
    'base_uri' => "{$apiHost}/",
]);

function createScreenGlCode(){
    global $client;
    $name ='GL Code screen 01';
    $response = $client->get('screens/?filter='.$name);
    $result = json_decode($response->getBody()->getContents(), true)['data'];
    return json_decode($response->getBody(), true)['data'][0]['id'];
}
//create a viwer GL Code
function createViewGlCode(){
    global $client;
    $name ='GL Code View 01';
    $response = $client->get('screens/?filter='.$name);
    $result = json_decode($response->getBody()->getContents(), true)['data'];
    return json_decode($response->getBody(), true)['data'][0]['id'];
}

//create a collection GL Code
function createCollectionGlCode($editScreen, $viewScreen){
    global $client;
    $name ='New GL Codes 01';
    $response = $client->get('collections/?filter='.$name);
    $result = json_decode($response->getBody(), true)['data'][0]['id'];
    //verify if the screen exist
    if (empty($result)){
        try{
            $response = $client->post('collections',[
                'json' => [
                    "name" => "New GL Codes 01",
                    "description" => "GL Codes creation",
                    "custom_title" => "New GL Codes 01",
                    "create_screen_id" => $data['editScreen']?? createScreenGlCode(),
                    "read_screen_id" => $data['viewScreen']?? createViewGlCode(),
                    "update_screen_id" => $data['editScreen']?? createScreenGlCode(),
                    "signal_create" => true,
                    "signal_update" => true,
                    "signal_delete" => true,
                ]
            ]);
        }catch(Exception $e) {
            return null;
        }
    }else{
        return json_decode($response->getBody(), true)['data'][0]['id'];
    }
}

$approval='';
function validateUserRolesbyArray($users, $requiredRoles) {
    $userRoles = array_map(function($user) {
        return $user['userRole'];
    },$users);
    $missingRoles = [];
    foreach ($requiredRoles as $role) {
        if (!in_array($role, $userRoles)) {
            $missingRoles[] = $role;
        }
    }
    return $missingRoles;
}
function readCsvFile($csvFile) {
    $users = [];
    $file = $apiInstance->getRequestFilesById($processRequestId, $fileId);
    $file = fopen($file->getPathname(), "r");
    if (($handle = $file) !== FALSE) {
        $header = fgetcsv($handle, 1000, ',');
        while (($data = fgetcsv($handle, 1000, ',')) !== FALSE) {
            $users[] = array_combine($header, $data);
        }
        fclose($handle);
    }
    return $users;
}

function validateUserRolesbyFile($users, $requiredRoles) {
    $userRoles = array_map(function($user) {
        return $user['userRole'];
    }, $users);
    $missingRoles = [];
    foreach ($requiredRoles as $role) {
        if (!in_array($role, $userRoles)) {
            $missingRoles[] = $role;
        }
    }
    return $missingRoles;
}

function getGroupId($groupName){
    global $api;
    $result = $api->groups()->getGroups('ACTIVE', $groupName);
    if(is_array($result->getData()) && count($result->getData())>0){
        return $result->getData()[0]->getId();
    }else{
        $group = new \ProcessMaker\Client\Model\GroupsEditable();
        $group->setName($groupName);
        $group->setDescription('');
        $group->setStatus('ACTIVE');
        return $api->groups()->createGroup($group)->getId();
    }
}

function addGroupMembers($users, $groups){
    global $api;
    $updateUserGroups = new \ProcessMaker\Client\Model\UpdateUserGroups();
    $invitedUsers = [];
    foreach($users as $user){
        $result = $api->users()->getUsers('ACTIVE', $user['userEmail']);
        if(is_array($result->getData()) && count($result->getData())>0){
            $userId = $result->getData()[0]->getId();
            $currentGroups = [];
            $result = $api->groupMembers()->getGroupMembers($userId);
            foreach($result->getData() as $group){
                $currentGroups[] = $group['group_id'];
            }
            if(!in_array($groups[$user['userRole']], $currentGroups)){
                $currentGroups[] = $groups[$user['userRole']];
            }
            $updateUserGroups->setGroups($currentGroups);
        }else{
            $newUser = new \ProcessMaker\Client\Model\UsersEditable();
            $newUser->setFirstname($user['userName']);
            $newUser->setLastname($user['userLastName']);
            $newUser->setUsername($user['userEmail']);
            $newUser->setPassword('SASWDWgh_1524');
            $newUser->setEmail($user['userEmail']);
            $newUser->setStatus('ACTIVE');
            $userId = $api->users()->createUser($newUser)->getId();
            $invitedUsers[] = ['id' => $userId, 'name' => $user['userName'].' '.$user['userLastName'], 'email' => $user['userEmail'], 'role' => $user['userRole']];
            $updateUserGroups->setGroups([$groups[$user['userRole']]]);
        }
        $api->users()->updateUserGroups($userId, $updateUserGroups);
    }
    return $invitedUsers;
}

$requiredRoles = ['invoice_creator', 'invoice_reviewer', 'finance_approver'];
$case = $data["fill_user"];
switch ($case): 
    case 'manual':
        $newUsers = $data['users'];
        $missingRoles = validateUserRolesbyArray($newUsers, $requiredRoles);
        if (empty($missingRoles)) {
            $approval = 'done';
            $errorMessage = 'It has the required roles.';
            $invitedUsers = false;
        } else {
            $approval = 'fail';
            return ['errorMessage' => 'missing roles: ' . implode(', ', $missingRoles) . '.', 'approval'=>$approval, 'invitedUsers' => false];
        }
        break;

    case 'upload': 
        $apiInstance = $api->requestFiles();
        $processRequestId = $data["_request"]["id"];
        $fileId = $data["file_upload_1"];
        $includeFirstRow = $data["includeFirstRow"];
        $file = $apiInstance->getRequestFilesById($processRequestId, $fileId);
        $fileContents = file_get_contents($file->getPathname());
        $csv = explode("\n",$fileContents);
        $cont=0;
        $newUsers = [];
        foreach($csv as $key){
            if($cont>0){
                $csv1 = explode(",",$key);
                $var = preg_replace("/\r|\n/", "", $csv1[3]);
                $newUsers[] = [
                    'userName' => preg_replace("/\r|\n/", "", $csv1[0]),
                    'userLastName' => preg_replace("/\r|\n/", "", $csv1[1]),
                    'userEmail' => preg_replace("/\r|\n/", "", $csv1[2]),
                    'userRole' => preg_replace("/\r|\n/", "", $csv1[3]),
                ];
                $clave[] = array_search($var, $requiredRoles); // $clave = 2;
            }
            //echo $key;
            $cont++;  
        }
        //return $clave;
        $requiredValues = [0, 1, 2];
        $foundValues = array_intersect($requiredValues, $clave);
        if (count($foundValues) === count($requiredValues)) {
            $approval = 'done';
            $errorMessage = 'It has the required roles.';
            $invitedUsers = false;
        } 
        else {
            $approval = 'fail';
            return ['errorMessage' => 'It dose not have the required roles.', 'approval' => $approval, 'invitedUsers' => false];
        }
        break;

    default:
        return ['errorMessage' => 'selection is not correct', 'approval'=>'fail', 'invitedUsers' => false];
endswitch;
$userGroups = [];
foreach($requiredRoles as $role){
    $userGroups[$role] = getGroupId($role);
}
$invitedUsers = addGroupMembers($newUsers, $userGroups);

return ['userGroups'=>$userGroups, 'approval'=>$approval, 'sendInvites' => (is_array($invitedUsers)&&count($invitedUsers)>0), 'invitedUsers' => $invitedUsers, 'errorMessage'=>$errorMessage, 'glCollection' => createCollectionGlCode($editScreen, $viewScreen)];

//Fill Data using switch
$case = $data["fill_glcode"];
switch ($case):
    case 'manual':
        // Truncate Collection
        $apiInstance = $api->collections();
        $collection_id = $creationGlCodeCollection;
        $apiInstance->truncateCollection($collection_id);
        //save data
        $codesGL = $data['codesGL'];
        $num = count($codesGL);
        if($num > 0){
            for($i = 0; $i <$num; $i++){
                createGLCodeRecord($codesGL[$i], $creationGlCodeCollection);
            }
            return ["glCodeIdCollection" => $creationGlCodeCollection, "approvalgl" => "done", "errorMessageCode" => 'ok'];
        }else{
            return ["errorMessageCode" => "At least one GL Code should be specified", "approvalgl" => "fail"];
        }
            
        break;
    case 'upload':
            // Truncate Collection
            $apiInstance = $api->collections();
            $collection_id = $creationGlCodeCollection;
            $apiInstance->truncateCollection($collection_id);
            // Uploaded file 
            $apiInstance = $api->requestFiles();
            $processRequestId = $data["_request"]["id"];
            $fileId = $data["file_upload_2"];
            $includeFirstRow = $data["includeFirstRow"];
            $file = $apiInstance->getRequestFilesById($processRequestId, $fileId);
            //$fileContents = file_get_contents($file->getPathname());
            $file = fopen($file->getPathname(), "r");
            try {// Open the file for reading
                if (($handle = $file) !== FALSE) {
                    $rowCount = 0;
                    // Loop through the CSV rows
                    while (($data = fgetcsv($handle, 1000, ',')) !== FALSE) {
                         $rowCount++;
                        // Ensure the CSV row has exactly 3 columns
                        if (count($data) == 2) {
                            // Create a record in the collection
                            $recordData = array(
                                'glcode' => $data[0], // Change 'field1', 'field2', 'field3' to your collection field names
                                'description' => $data[1]
                            );
                            if($rowCount>1){
                                createGLCodeRecord($recordData, $creationGlCodeCollection);
                            }
                        }else{// Handle error: CSV row does not have 2 columns
                            return ["errorMessageCode" => "At least one GL Code should be specified", "approvalgl" => "fail"];
                        }
                    }// Close the file
                    fclose($handle);
                    if ($rowCount >= 2) {
                            return ["glCodeIdCollection" => $creationGlCodeCollection, "approvalgl" => "done"];
                        } else {
                            return ["errorMessageCode" => "At least one GL Code should be specified", "approvalgl" => "fail"];
                        }
                }else{// Handle error: unable to open file
                    return ["errorMessageCode" => "At least one GL Code should be specified", "approvalgl" => "fail"];
                }
            }catch (Exception $e) {
                return[("errorMessageCode: " . $e->getMessage()), "approvalgl" => "fail"];
            }
        break;
    default:
        return ["errorMessageCode" => "selection is not correct", "approvalgl" => "fail"];
endswitch;

<?php 

use GuzzleHttp\Client;
use GuzzleHttp\Exception\BadResponseException;
$apiHost = getenv('API_HOST');
$apiToken = getenv('API_TOKEN');

$client = new Client([
    'headers' => [
        'Authorization' => "Bearer {$apiToken}",
        'accept' => 'application/json',
    ],
    'base_uri' => "{$apiHost}/",
]);
// screen fields here
$screenData = [
    "title" => "GL Code screen 01",
    "type" => "FORM",
    "description" => "GL Code Screen description",
    "projects" => [],
    "screen_category_id" => "1",
];
// screen view fields here
$screenViewData = [
    "title" => "GL Code View 01",
    "type" => "DISPLAY",
    "description" => "GL Code View description",
    "projects" => [],
    "screen_category_id" => "1",
];
//createa a new screen adn view Screen
$editScreen = createScreenGlCode($screenData);
$viewScreen = createViewGlCode($screenViewData);

return [
    "editScreen" => $editScreen,
    "viewScreen" => $viewScreen
];

//create a screen GL Code
function createScreenGlCode($screenData){
    global $client;
    $name ='GL Code screen 01';
    $response = $client->get('screens/?filter='.$name);
    $result = json_decode($response->getBody()->getContents(), true)['data'];
    //verify if the screen exist
    if(count($result)>0){
        return json_decode($response->getBody(), true)['data'][0]['id'];
    }else{
        $response = $client->post('screens/',[
                    'json' => $screenData
        ]);
        return json_decode($response->getBody(), true)['data'][0]['id'];
    }
}
//create a viwer GL Code
function createViewGlCode($screenViewData){
    global $client;
    $name ='GL Code View 01';
    $response = $client->get('screens/?filter='.$name);
    $result = json_decode($response->getBody()->getContents(), true)['data'];
    //verify if the screen exist
    if(count($result)>0){
        return json_decode($response->getBody(), true)['data'][0]['id'];
    }else{
        $response = $client->post('screens/',[
            'json' => $screenViewData
        ]);
        return json_decode($response->getBody(), true)['data'][0]['id'];
    }
}
